Package SchedulingSystem

Class SchedulingSystem

java.lang.Object
SchedulingSystem.SchedulingSystem
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SchedulingSystem
extends Object
implements Serializable
Class that is utilized throughout the program. It is used to keep track of all available courses, to keep track of the current student running the system, and managing the countdown timer.
Author:
Kevin Wang
